{"tid":1926923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎》對抗新型冠狀病毒 以色列將採用台灣經驗！","createTime":"2020-03-15T12:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T13:01:07.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"55ba6a905889b2b495a4ade30efea011329d5503","tid":1926923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎》對抗新型冠狀病毒 以色列將採用台灣經驗！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3100327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100327&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=44fcf3cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3100327&h=9fa75386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3100327</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以色列總理納坦雅胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）表示，政府將遵循台灣經驗來對抗武漢肺炎疫情，同時也計劃使用反恐追蹤技術，盡可能降低新型冠狀病毒傳播的風險。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，納坦雅胡在新聞發布會上表示，新型冠狀病毒是一種隱形的敵人，但無論如何都要將它找出來，以色列將參考台灣防疫經驗並採取類似方法來應對。<br />\n<br />\n納坦雅胡也宣布，商場、飯店、餐廳、劇院今（15日）開始全面關閉，員工在有必要的情況下才需要去上班，不過，藥局、超市和銀行等提供重要服務的場所會繼續營業。另外，自上個星期以來，任何進入以色列的旅客都必須自我隔離14天。<br />\n<br />\n以色列還將透過網路監控技術來定位曾和確診者密切接觸的民眾，該技術過去一直是打擊恐怖主義的利器，但使用在目前的狀況下可能會侵犯患者隱私，所以還需要司法部批准才能實施。<br />\n<br />\n以色列國家安全局證實，因應納坦雅胡和衛生部的要求，該局正在研究與新型冠狀病毒對抗的技術。以國人權協會的個人隱私專家平恰克（Avner Pinchuk）表示，這種技術可能包括隨時追蹤感染者的手機以發現隔離漏洞，並透過數據回溯他們曾到過哪些地方、和哪些人接觸過。<br />\n<br />\n納坦雅胡說，在他擔任總理的這些年當中，他一直避免在平民中使用這類監控手段，但現在已別無選擇。目前以色列有193起確診病例，成千上萬的國民被隔離。"},{"pid":"2081e5a39051659b25632300890ca03c42c88482","tid":1926923,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"台灣經驗+以色列反恐=完美"},{"pid":"957b3edaccfc1f44fd8623d0660b09b2b8646c79","tid":1926923,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:32:15.000Z","msg":"台灣NO.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dcb039274b0809c91b3b9e963561de5474828f","tid":1926923,"uid":25183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎病毒升lv成恐怖份子"},{"pid":"5115ed889ba847b19c8616029ba004b3c705f11e","tid":1926923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2081e5a39051659b25632300890ca03c42c88482","tid":1926923,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"台灣經驗+以色列反恐=完美"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"睇時香港學到佢哋個套就好"},{"pid":"92747f39be33c76e718d0c4018432f26d770d44f","tid":1926923,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"WHO只係成日讚中國大陸點好點好, 完全當台灣透明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b002fcb72b0dc4d915d2f7c8234cd48b3c95057a","tid":1926923,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"猶太人認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}